{"tid":1466590,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"機場 化解方法 請睇睇","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:37.000Z","uid":162393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a361576efd6a24d0db295581e028a2b79c64361c","tid":1466590,"uid":162393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:07.000Z","msg":"問：阻塞機場搞死香港？<br />\n答：「做法不完美，但可接受，可以再改善。」<br />\n<br />\n問：點解阻止公安離開？<br />\n答：「佢唔喺現場出現就冇事，去得果度就可能有呢啲風險」。<br />\n<br />\n問：阻止救護帶佢離開？人命嚟㗎。<br />\n答：「而家眾說紛云，我認為事主可以去報警先，警方必定會跟進調查。」<br />\n<br />\n問：點解你地咁冇人性，濫用暴力，究竟想點？<br />\n「在場嘅市民只係用最低武力，當一切平靜後，真誠對話就會展開。」<br />\n<br />\n對唔住，7.21、8.11血仍未乾，有人爆頭，有人失明，有人俾黑警打到成地血都冇收手，之後我從來冇聽過，警方有道歉有撤查。<br />\n<br />\n以上，全部係黑警同林奠嘅對白，香港人已經好克制了。<br />\n<br />\n人命？你睇俾黑警打到成地血嘅義士個樣，同埋呢個公安？現場有一句，喺大陸，你死撚咗啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J34udcw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ34udcw.jpg&h=ffae6a7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HJXohEd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHJXohEd.jpg&h=5b434813&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kF96fqU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkF96fqU.jpg&h=e48b9da3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#不割席<br />\n#不篤灰<br />\n#不分化"},{"pid":"5b7b6a48c85f8f856a3a9fb9965be369d11c6f17","tid":1466590,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f040632f2e1a7c38edb318281713e079bab555c","tid":1466590,"uid":162393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"747f70446bac8e1ac04f85218326dac3a42b1565","tid":1466590,"uid":162393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:02.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"29b440b4881d5d42e352a24914124280be2edcd1","tid":1466590,"uid":108902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:37.000Z","msg":"［文宣煲大佢］有疑似黑社會入機場踩線搞恐襲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1465124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1465124</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我地已經冇可能再割蓆"}]}